{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1797052, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者“小时候得过多囊卵巢，不能生育”，这样说人家会不会觉得太极端？", "timestamp": 1622957900, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797076, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以反问他“怎么你要根据我的婚育计划选择是否录取我吗”吗", "timestamp": 1622958126, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797086, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": 1797076, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 啊这，硬钢当然爽，但人也要生活.", "timestamp": 1622958242, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797088, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "问问有啥影响，搞歧视就让他爬", "timestamp": 1622958263, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797107, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": 1797088, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不是，公司肯定不会直接承认吧，你反问的话公司最多是笑笑，“我们不过就是问一问”。只是问一问，你就算举报，也是不了了之\n不录取一个人，没必要说理由，甚至可以扯其他你不优秀的理由.", "timestamp": 1622958488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797108, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": 1797088, "tag": null, "text": "只是单纯想请教一下话术", "timestamp": 1622958506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797171, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "目前没有计划。我觉得就挺好，如果还追问的公司，不去也罢", "timestamp": 1622959760, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1797307, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 353076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果想去的话，就说暂时没有计划，不想去觉得问题恶心的话，就说暂时没考虑好，既然贵公司提出了这个问题，我可以去学校论坛上问问大家的规划", "timestamp": 1622962385, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 353076, "reply": 8